### Welcome to ZecWeekly
Hello ZCashers!!! Welcome to another part of ZecWeekly where we share recent news, updates and beneficial information in both the Crypto Space and ZCash Ecosystem. This week newsletter will be covering recent occurrence that happened in the Cryptocurrency space including the outcome of the ZCash Aborist Call and some vital information about ZCash and it's ecosystem without leaving out our educational piece of the week where you get to learn and understand some important tips when it comes to exploring ZCash. 

---

## This week's education piece
There's definitely no doubt that the ZCash ecosystem is drastically increasing more than we can ever imagine with lot of Decentralized Applications being developed on the ZCash Blockchain. The adoption of Zero Knowledge (Zk) in cryptography has led to the Zingolabs team to develop a complete Shielded ZCash application known as Zingo Wallet. 

The Zingo Wallet App supports Funding Pools such as Orchard, Sampling and Transparent wallet transaction between other ZCash wallets. You can learn more about Zingo Wallet and it's features via the below link;

[Zingo! A ZCash Application] (https://free2z.cash/zingolabs/zpage/zingo-a-zcash-application) 







